OL,3,CFamily's plea after woman killed by
OL,4,Clorry driver using mobile phone
OL,6,FThe family of a woman killed by a
OL,7,Fdistracted lorry driver have issued a
OL,8,Fplea to motorists to not use their
OL,9,Fmobile phone at the wheel.
OL,11,FAlex Britton, Tina Ince and Tom Watson
OL,12,Fwere killed in a catastrophic incident
OL,13,Fon the A303 near Andover on 25 August
OL,14,F2021.
