OL,6,FAaron Law, Alex's fiance, said: "One
OL,7,Fof the most devastating things I've
OL,8,Fever done is break the news to my, at
OL,9,Fthe time, three year old daughter that
OL,10,Fher mummy wasn't coming back home.
OL,11,F"Being only three we thought she would
OL,12,Ffind it hard to understand, but
OL,13,Finstantly she grasped what was going
OL,14,Fon and she broke down in tears.J"I
OL,15,Fnever planned to raise two children by
OL,16,Fmyself. We planned to do it as a
OL,17,Ffamily. I now struggle every day with
OL,18,Fsimple tasks. There's just certain
OL,19,Fthings that I can't teach them, that
OL,20,Fmummy would have taught them."
