OL,4,Clorry driver using mobile phone
OL,6,FAfter Alex's car broke down on the
OL,7,Fwestbound carriageway, Tina and Tom
OL,8,Fboth stopped to offer her assistance.
OL,9,FBut lorry driver, who was watching
OL,10,Fvideos and typing in his destination
OL,11,Fon his phone, did not see the three
OL,12,Fstationary vehicles ahead of him and
OL,13,Fcrashed into them. All three victims
OL,14,Fwere killed instantly.
